OL,3,CDisappeared victim's son criticises
OL,4,C'cruel' depiction of mother's death in
OL,5,Cdrama
OL,7,FThe son of a woman murdered and
OL,8,Fsecretly buried by the IRA has called
OL,9,Fthe portrayal of her death in a new
OL,10,Fdrama series "cruel".
OL,12,FMichael McConville, who was a child in
OL,13,F1972 when his mother Jean was abducted
OL,14,Ffrom their west Belfast home, said her
OL,15,Fdeath is "not entertainment" but his
OL,16,Fand his family's reality for the last
OL,17,F52 years.
