OL,7,FMrs McConville is known as one of the
OL,8,FDisappeared, a group of 17 people who
OL,9,Fwere abducted, killed and secretly
OL,10,Fburied by republican paramilitaries
OL,11,Fduring the Troubles.
OL,13,FHer remains were finally found in 2003
OL,14,Fat Shelling Hill Beach in Co Louth in
OL,15,Fthe Irish Republic by the Independent
OL,16,FCommission for the Location of
OL,17,FVictims' Remains (ICLVR).
OL,19,FNo one has ever been prosecuted over
OL,20,Fher death which left 10 children
OL,21,Forphaned.
