OL,7,FHe said he has not watched the series
OL,8,Fand does not intend to.
OL,10,F"Disney is renowned for entertainment,
OL,11,Fmy mother's death is not
OL,12,F'entertainment' for me and my family,"
OL,13,Fhe said in a statement on Wednesday
OL,14,Fevening.
OL,16,F"This is our reality, every day for 52
OL,17,Fyears.
