OL,3,CDisappeared victim's son criticises
OL,4,C'cruel' depiction of mother's death in
OL,5,Cdrama
OL,7,F"And although we live with it every
OL,8,Fsingle day and it never goes away, the
OL,9,Ftiming of this is particularly bad
OL,10,Fgiven that it is my mother's
OL,11,Fanniversary on December 1."
OL,13,F"I just don't think people realise how
OL,14,Fhurtful this is."
OL,16,FHe added: "The portrayal of the
OL,17,Fexecution and secret burial of my
OL,18,Fmother is horrendous and unless you
OL,19,Fhave lived through it, you will never
OL,20,Funderstand just how cruel it is.
