OL,3,CDisappeared victim's son criticises
OL,4,C'cruel' depiction of mother's death in
OL,5,Cdrama
OL,7,F"Everyone knows the story of Jean
OL,8,FMcConville, even Hillary Clinton who I
OL,9,Fmet a few years ago knew my mother's
OL,10,Fstory.
OL,12,F"And yet here is another telling of it
OL,13,Fthat I and my family have to endure.
OL,15,F"Eventually, this series will be
OL,16,Fforgotten and the people who made it
OL,17,Fwill have moved on to something else.
OL,19,F"They can do that, I can't."
